topPRs.title: Add tokenomics page with contract addresses and vesting details
topPRs.author: wtfsayo
topPRs.body:
## Changes

This PR adds comprehensive tokenomics documentation to the ElizaOS docs.

### What's Changed
- ‚ú® Created new  page with detailed token information
- üìë Added tokenomics to sidebar navigation under Getting Started section
- üè∑Ô∏è Added prominent banner card on home page linking to tokenomics page

### Content Included
- Contract addresses for SVM (Solana) and EVM (Ethereum, Base, BSC) chains
- Token standards and cross-chain capabilities (CCIP enabled)
- Total and circulating supply information
- Detailed vesting schedules for all allocations (Ecosystem, Foundation, Team, SAFT, Liquidity)
- Token release schedule and migration details from $ai16z to $elizaOS
- Change log documenting key dates

### Documentation Best Practices
- Uses Mintlify components (Card, Steps, Info, Note, Warning) for better UX
- Follows MDX formatting standards with proper frontmatter
- Includes descriptive icon (coins) for visual consistency
- Maintains consistent styling with existing documentation
